f=Engineering/nova/operational/tool/nova-tool-requirements.md · p=What nova needs, what happens without each. conditional `mobile_active` (dormant otherwise). external tool call plan-locked (Rail sandboxed (Rail 2); nova runs data changes (Rail 3). · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\| Need \| Tool / access \| Used by \| Without it \| · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\| Repo read/write for mobile code \| repo scope (per stack-profile) \| all skills \| Core; without write, design-only \| · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\| Mobile framework + build toolchain \| Flutter/RN/native SDK (per stack-profile) \| mobile-app-architecture, release \| Method-only guidance \| · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\| Real-device farm / physical devices \| per stack-profile \| mobile-verification \| Widest available devices + emulator, labeled; never a release verdict \| · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\| Local persistence + secure storage \| Keychain/Keystore via framework \| offline-sync-discipline \| Sensitive data can't be secured — blocks the feature \| · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\| App store connect / play console access \| store APIs \| app-store-release-discipline \| Manual submission by operator; nova prepares, operator submits + signs \| · h2:Requirements (only when mobile_active)=\| Server API access \| raj's API contracts \| offline-sync-discipline \| Can't sync; escalate \| · h2:Explicit non-needs hard prohibitions (by design)=**Signing keys/certs OPERATOR-held** nova never holds uses them leaked signing key catastrophic)., **No data change execution** server data changes dana's operator-run migrations (Rail 3); sync goes through raj's validating API, never direct bypass., **No activation web-only businesses** mobile_active false dormant, full stop., **No secrets app bundle** anything shipped app extractable (aegis). · n=nova builder code